Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.14,0:00:28.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Wi...With Mt. Ontake as the only clue, this place is too vast to search on foot.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.63,0:00:32.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Just how much farther {\i0}is{\i1} it from here?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.00,0:00:36.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Kuromaro-donooooo!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.32,0:00:51.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanami?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.16,0:00:55.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing in a place like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.06,0:00:59.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Yukiji-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.54,0:01:05.54,Title,,0,0,0,,{\pos(320,435)}The God\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N Becomes a Bride
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.02,0:01:07.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Himetaro isn't with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.51,0:01:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard that on the day you left, he disappeared too.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.50,0:01:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,So I thought for certain that he must have left with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.50,0:01:20.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'm sorry... for leaving without saying a word.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.88,0:01:27.43,sign2,,0,0,0,,{\move(670,320,645,290)\frz 10\fade(0,1500)}Himetarou
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.30,0:01:23.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tomoe also left the house that day...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.26,0:01:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I wonder if his fate was properly linked to Yukiji-san...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.42,0:01:30.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you here in the capital, Yukiji-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.78,0:01:35.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Have you perhaps settled your marriage negotiations with that rich man here?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.44,0:01:38.08,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\pos(778,250)}Crack
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.34,0:01:37.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Rich man?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.57,0:01:40.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you mean that old lecher?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.96,0:01:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,He pounced on me out of nowhere when I went to meet him,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.36,0:01:46.82,Default,,0,0,0,,so I kicked his face with all my might!~
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.66,0:01:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,But thanks to that, I received a better proposal.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.76,0:01:55.19,Default,,0,0,0,,The wedding is being arranged to be held very soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.76,0:01:59.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I came to the capital to choose things for my trousseau.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.74,0:02:00.82,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.58,0:02:06.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yukiji-san will now be duly wed into a lord's family~
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.28,0:02:08.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Nanami, it's you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.36,0:02:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Fuuta-kun!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.03,0:02:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Stupid Nanami, what have you been up to till now!?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.34,0:02:15.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Could this miss be...?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.60,0:02:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You!! You're from that bunch who treated me rudely the other time!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.66,0:02:22.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Suke.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.03,0:02:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,This time I've come as Yukiji-san's attendant.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.77,0:02:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Sukeroku, did you reach an agreement at the draper?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.22,0:02:30.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.29,0:02:34.24,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll leave here and return to the village tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.57,0:02:35.51,Default,,0,0,0,,What about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.66,0:02:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Umm... Please let me accompany you on your way home.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.01,0:02:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll go to the mountain up north of the village,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.77,0:02:47.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and have Kappa-san call for Kuromaru once again.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.74,0:02:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's definitely more reliable.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.15,0:02:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, I don't mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.53,0:02:55.57,Default,,0,0,0,,But don't vanish on your whim this time, Nanami.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.55,0:02:57.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to take a bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.91,0:02:59.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.77,0:03:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yukiji-san will be marrying a lord!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.52,0:03:09.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Stop, stop! Don't think of needless things.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.66,0:03:12.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Nothing I think here will change anything!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.09,0:03:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,,My lady... Her home was burned by youkai and she became an orphan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.16,0:03:24.19,Default,,0,0,0,,But Master, who appraised her looks to be useful, took her in as his daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.04,0:03:29.66,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why he was very happy with this most desirable marriage offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.12,0:03:35.05,Default,,0,0,0,,But, I think that Yukiji-sama was the happiest when she learned about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.08,0:03:38.31,Default,,0,0,0,,"With this, I'll finally leave this house."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.70,0:03:42.01,Default,,0,0,0,,"I'll finally create a real family of my own", she said.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.11,0:03:46.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I want Yukiji-sama to be happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.39,0:03:49.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Because she has suffered a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.18,0:03:51.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.18,0:03:54.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm an outsider.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.22,0:03:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Still, it is alright to pray for her happiness?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.50,0:04:03.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Yukiji!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.56,0:04:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Where in the world where you dawdling about!?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.40,0:04:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,And even when I said the lord's envoys will be here soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.64,0:04:11.53,Default,,0,0,0,,And you've gotten so filthy...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.76,0:04:14.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Go bathe and rinse off that filth from your trip!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.00,0:04:17.37,Default,,0,0,0,,The procession is already tomorrow, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.77,0:04:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.54,0:04:23.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yukiji-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.44,0:04:28.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Kappa-san's mountain has somehow gotten pitch black.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.54,0:04:32.11,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Would it be possible for me to stay here tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.39,0:04:34.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kappa-san was...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.80,0:04:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...no longer there.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.84,0:04:41.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Kuromaro-dono will come immediately when I call him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.62,0:04:46.76,Default,,0,0,0,,When he comes, this pond will probably be tainted with black and become uninhabitable.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.07,0:04:52.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}At that time, it was because we called for Kuromaro that the mountain became black.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.48,0:04:56.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't call him just like that.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.93,0:04:58.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If I don't leave this place...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.29,0:05:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I... will bring upon something terrible...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.61,0:05:07.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What is a good way to reach Mt. Ontake?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.48,0:05:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanami.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.17,0:05:11.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.40,0:05:19.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Fuuta-kun, where's Yukiji-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.59,0:05:22.25,Default,,0,0,0,,She's preparing for tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.41,0:05:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Leaving that aside, I thought you were a dark monster earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.22,0:05:27.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Um?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.04,0:05:28.81,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.67,0:05:33.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you Yukiji?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.26,0:05:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Youkai!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.80,0:05:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Akura-ou-sama wants you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.99,0:05:51.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn you, attacking from behind, what sort of a defiant attitude is that!?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.52,0:05:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What in the world is all that commotion!?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.55,0:05:56.85,Default,,0,0,0,,My Lady!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.98,0:05:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You belong to Akura-ou-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.92,0:06:04.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't think your procession will go smoothly!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.30,0:06:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Akura-ou!?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.87,0:06:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Yukiji! Stop this, Yukiji!!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.64,0:06:10.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.50,0:06:13.69,Default,,0,0,0,,This has to be cleaned quickly. Do it secretly!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.96,0:06:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.59,0:06:17.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yukiji-san...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.68,0:06:23.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow is the bridal procession already. Just what are we to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.51,0:06:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It's too late to postpone it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.96,0:06:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Being tactless will send my head flying!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.45,0:06:30.93,Default,,0,0,0,,As planned, she will depart tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.10,0:06:33.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You're fine with this too, aren't you, Yukiji?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.40,0:06:34.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, father.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.36,0:06:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It's dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.82,0:06:39.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Please reconsider tomorrow's procession!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.33,0:06:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,This Akura-ou who's targeting Yukiji-san, isn't just some youkai!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.36,0:06:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this? Outsider's should stay quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.25,0:06:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,She might get killed!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.26,0:06:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,If that happens, then so be it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.73,0:06:57.22,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing to do except leave her fate to the heavens!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.49,0:06:58.39,Default,,0,0,0,,No way...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.53,0:06:59.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Nanami,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.56,0:07:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm going to make a family of my own blood.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.05,0:07:05.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm going to be happy.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.40,0:07:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I must protect her!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.76,0:07:10.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If it's for the sake of Yukiji-san's happy smile,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.48,0:07:13.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be her substitute.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.56,0:07:16.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be Yukiji-san's substitute and ride the palanquin.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.73,0:07:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What stupid things are you saying!?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.56,0:07:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanami, as if I'd let you pretend to be me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.14,0:07:23.89,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a good plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.76,0:07:27.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You have nearly the same built as Yukiji. This might go well.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.07,0:07:29.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Father...!?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.00,0:07:31.22,Default,,0,0,0,,In return,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.64,0:07:36.07,Default,,0,0,0,,while I'm acting as her stand-in, I want you to search for a certain someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.73,0:07:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I want you to utilize all the men and horses you employ,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.08,0:07:43.61,Default,,0,0,0,,to deliver my words to {\i1}him{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.55,0:07:50.24,Default,,0,0,0,,He is a fallen god who resides on Mt. Ontake. His name is Kuromaro.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.16,0:07:49.92,sign2,,0,0,0,,{\pos(200,440)}To Mt. Ontake's\NKuromaro
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.00,0:08:01.71,Default,,0,0,0,,And also, this white paper will guide you to wherever he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.89,0:08:04.23,Default,,0,0,0,,These are my terms for being her stand-in.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.07,0:08:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm going to save both Yukiji-san and Tomoe.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.40,0:08:08.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is my best strategy!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.14,0:08:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright. I'll prepare my men and horses.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.25,0:08:17.45,Default,,0,0,0,,However, there's no assurance of your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.68,0:08:21.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}From the start, I didn't come here with a half-hearted resolve.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.14,0:08:27.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's abandon this castle already.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.98,0:08:31.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It's built on a cliff, so descending from it is bothersome.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.54,0:08:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,And the sound of wind within the castle is loud too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.56,0:08:36.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you tired of it already, Akura-ou?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.00,0:08:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though you said this castle-on-the cliff was cool and killed the owner to get it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.58,0:08:45.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, how about moving to the sea next?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.04,0:08:49.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems like the Dragon King and his palace reside in the ocean depths of the west.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.04,0:08:51.61,Default,,0,0,0,,The Dragon King, huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.08,0:08:53.56,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a good idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.00,0:08:57.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard that the Dragon King's eyes are pills of immortality.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.40,0:09:01.94,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case, we'll split them evenly.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.80,0:09:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Right eye mine, left eye yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.75,0:09:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds fun, eh brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.83,0:09:11.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You've finally returned to your usual self.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.32,0:09:20.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmmmm~? Who is it that put this mop in a place like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.38,0:09:28.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you been in excellent spirits, Akura-ou-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.43,0:09:35.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Your faithful servant, Kirakaburi, has returned from Izumo.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.91,0:09:41.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Ohh, Kirakaburi, I have an errand for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.17,0:09:44.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! What could it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.75,0:09:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems like a human woman named Yukiji will have her bridal procession tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.23,0:09:53.32,Default,,0,0,0,,The guy I sent earlier failed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.87,0:09:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,They say she's extraordinarily beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.44,0:09:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to see her face.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.92,0:10:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Hee~! Hearing she's a beauty has gotten me fired up. Do you only want her face?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.72,0:10:06.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Except her face, I don't care about the rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.69,0:10:08.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if it means she can't move.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.84,0:10:16.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, this producer of beauty, Kirakaburi, will use all his skills and see to it that your expectations are met.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.93,0:10:19.76,Default,,0,0,0,,So, where is this young woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.01,0:10:22.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Ask all the trivial stuff to that furball over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.56,0:10:24.44,Default,,0,0,0,,All the information is from him after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.49,0:10:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.44,0:10:26.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmph!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.21,0:10:34.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What is this feeling?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.42,0:10:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.82,0:10:39.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going home to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.56,0:10:42.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Sweet dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.50,0:10:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I don't care!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.48,0:10:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's just no fun that the flower I failed to pick is going to be trampled by those guys.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.24,0:10:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's all.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.85,0:11:03.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it a bit too reckless?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.46,0:11:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,A youkai will certainly discover that it's not me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.86,0:11:08.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop with this talk about youkai already!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.18,0:11:13.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, I can't lose face before his lordship.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.32,0:11:17.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You better hold your tongue and do as I say!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.06,0:11:19.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}How horrible!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.29,0:11:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Master only thinks about protecting himself.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.86,0:11:24.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He doesn't care about my lady even a little bit!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.00,0:11:31.94,Default,,0,0,0,,But father, if the youkai see through the impostor, they might come to attack this mansion.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.98,0:11:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm!? True!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.26,0:11:38.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You're their target, so they must be knowing how beautiful you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.87,0:11:43.49,Default,,0,0,0,,A girl that filthy may not be able to fool them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.29,0:11:47.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Master, Nanami is ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.76,0:11:51.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Her loose, rumpled hair have been arranged.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.44,0:11:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,With this, she shall fill in suitably for Yukiji-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.52,0:12:01.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Why, she's barely recognizable!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.37,0:12:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,,To think that she'd resemble Yukiji this much! If it's like this, even the youkai can't suspect her!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.44,0:12:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Lady Yukiji and Nanami... I thought that they both had a vaguely similar aura, but I was wrong.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.49,0:12:17.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Their appearances alone are nearly the same.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.38,0:12:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Can two complete strangers look this alike?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.33,0:12:24.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Perhaps Nanami is Yukiji-sama's relative...?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.75,0:12:31.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Idiot! Did you think I would thank you for looking like that!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.32,0:12:34.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to be happy by letting you die!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.15,0:12:36.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a nuisance!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.65,0:12:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened to you suddenly? Speaking like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.52,0:12:42.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Lady Yukiji...?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.45,0:12:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I apologize for causing trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.63,0:12:47.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I want you to be happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.92,0:12:51.94,Default,,0,0,0,,But, just like you, I want to be happy as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.70,0:12:54.41,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I won't die.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.28,0:12:56.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.95,0:13:00.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanami...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.76,0:13:03.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't resemble me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.36,0:13:08.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't make that look in your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.64,0:13:16.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Eyes filled with hope... Facing ahead without despair, her eyes are without the slightest of doubt.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.25,0:13:20.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Yukiji-san's Papa, please promise that you'll also find Kuromaro, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.84,0:13:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I envy you, Nanami...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.89,0:13:31.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The next morning, Yukiji-san left the mansion quietly as planned.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.93,0:13:36.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Until Yukiji-san arrives at her husband lord's household safely, I'll catch their attention.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.29,0:13:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}For that, I'll roam around flamboyantly.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.16,0:13:44.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Though it's just a pretense, I never thought that I'd become a bride.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.72,0:13:46.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I wonder what Tomoe would say if he saw me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.19,0:13:48.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't suit you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.13,0:13:51.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Somehow I heard that!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.73,0:13:57.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll play a trick on that Akura-ou.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.81,0:14:00.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'd be lying if I said I'm not scared,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.68,0:14:05.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}but I have my white paper charms, the dagger I borrowed from Yukiji-san...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.14,0:14:08.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and... the hairpin from Tomoe.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.69,0:14:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Protect me, okay Tomoe?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.96,0:14:18.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Please, let everything go well.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.20,0:14:25.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Just what is wrong with me?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.61,0:14:28.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This impatience is keeping me from being calm.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.26,0:14:35.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So much so, that I failed to kill that young girl.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.89,0:14:40.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}All because I wasn't acting like usual, I wasn't in tune with myself.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.45,0:14:44.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If she's going to be finished off by those guys...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.37,0:14:49.43,Default,,0,0,0,,For once, I'll definitely kill her with my own hands next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.01,0:14:51.70,Default,,0,0,0,,This is getting interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.32,0:14:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,This is definitely... more like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.26,0:15:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanami-san, I'm tired already. My load is very heavy. Let's rest a bit in this area, Nanami-sa-
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.86,0:15:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It isn't Nanami, right!? It's Yukiji!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.18,0:15:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What are we going to do if the youkai hear it!?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.24,0:15:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yukiji-san wouldn't have hit me like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.31,0:15:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this fog?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.17,0:15:38.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Poison!?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.25,0:15:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no! Don't inhale this fog!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.53,0:15:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Apologies for making you wait, miss bride.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.14,0:15:53.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Kirakaburi, a creator for beauty.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.96,0:15:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,By Akura-ou-sama's orders, I've come to fetch you~
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.41,0:16:01.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You finally showed up, eh youkai!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.34,0:16:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's not Akura-ou! Looks kind of flashy!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.96,0:16:07.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn you, release Yukiji-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.29,0:16:14.71,Default,,0,0,0,,To think that miss bride's accessories are this shabby...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.98,0:16:18.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Even a beauty production has it's limits, you know~
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.68,0:16:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,For now, should I pulverize you all and sprinkle gold dust on you guys~?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.48,0:16:35.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it! Please don't kill them!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.44,0:16:39.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't defy you! I'll go to wherever Akura-ou is!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.51,0:16:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't mind if you defy me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.03,0:16:46.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Because after I've adorned them for their funeral, you will be next, Yukiji-dono.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.08,0:16:51.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Even the deceased are an embodiment of beauty.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.56,0:16:56.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It's my job to decorate you to the best of my ability and present you to Akura-ou-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.20,0:16:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You have the wrong person!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.68,0:17:02.19,Default,,0,0,0,,That person is not Yukiji-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.30,0:17:03.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Suke-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.47,0:17:06.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is bad! If this carries on, everyone's going to be killed!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.72,0:17:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm right here! Catch me if you can!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.00,0:17:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Heh! It's useless!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.34,0:17:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,And you're trying to escape from me with those legs...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.78,0:17:32.28,sign2,,0,0,0,,{\move(435,200,440,195)\frz -10}Nanami
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.25,0:17:32.14,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this!?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.85,0:17:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Running like this reminds me of that incident in Yomi.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.20,0:17:49.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's right, at that time, Tomoe had come to my rescue.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.91,0:18:04.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Right now, I'm... helplessly alone.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.56,0:18:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I want to see you...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.65,0:18:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tomoe!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.40,0:18:22.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't run away anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.72,0:18:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,That poison is a numbing drug I created.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.43,0:18:31.91,Default,,0,0,0,,First, your legs with rapidly become unmovable and your brain will cease to function in the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.01,0:18:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't move...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.15,0:18:42.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Am I going to die... without being able to see you... Tomoe?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.41,0:18:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,My bad, Kirakaburi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.97,0:19:02.05,Default,,0,0,0,,She is mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.09,0:19:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomoe...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.57,0:19:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What is the meaning of this, Fox-dono?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.15,0:19:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you plan to rebel against Akura-ou-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.88,0:19:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I am not his underling.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.60,0:19:21.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't group me with you bastards.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.29,0:19:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tomoe...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.50,0:19:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tomoe...!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.83,0:19:32.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tomoe...!!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.13,0:19:36.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I finally caught you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.22,0:19:40.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Now then, how shall I end your life?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.88,0:19:41.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tomoe!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.48,0:19:48.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The one holding me right now, isn't the Tomoe of the present.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.55,0:19:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's the terrifying Tomoe of 500 years ago.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.07,0:19:54.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But... he has the same smell.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.45,0:19:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If I could move my hands, I would be able to touch his hair,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.49,0:20:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}feel the heat of his body...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.98,0:20:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...more.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.26,0:20:16.36,Default,,0,0,0,,So you can't move your body due to the poison? How boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.97,0:20:18.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm scared!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.59,0:20:20.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, look over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.89,0:20:25.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Although I'm afraid, somewhere in my heart, a part of me doesn't reject it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.29,0:20:27.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.72,0:20:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tomoe's arms feel warm and good.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.96,0:20:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I wanted to meet him, I wanted to touch him like this, always.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.96,0:20:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at me, Yukiji.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.51,0:20:47.51,sign 3,,0,0,0,,{\pos(420,400)}Yukiji
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.26,0:20:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,No...!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.52,0:20:53.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Please! Don't look at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.76,0:20:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm not Yukiji.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.85,0:21:03.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I... look horrible right now! Don't look at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.21,0:21:08.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If I could move my arms right now, I would cover my face this instant.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.84,0:21:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I want to shout out that I'm not Yukiji and disappear from this place!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.02,0:21:17.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, Tomoe...!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.47,0:21:31.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't... weep like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.43,0:21:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,When you cry, I loose my nerves.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.22,0:21:42.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}From afar, I could hear the sound of rain.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.00,0:21:45.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Was everyone able to run to safety?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.37,0:21:48.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Adrift in the depths of darkness,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.92,0:21:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I saw a dream of Yukiji-san, surrounded by her new family, smiling happily.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.62,0:22:02.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't move my body.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.18,0:22:04.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Something is holding me down.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.78,0:22:06.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't squirm.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.72,0:22:08.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Just stay still like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.91,0:22:09.51,Default,,0,0,0,,To-
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.58,0:22:11.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up. Don't talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.46,0:22:13.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep sleeping till I wake up.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.32,0:22:22.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is this!? Why is Tomoe here!?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.92,0:22:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's right, I was attacked by a youkai yesterday during the procession...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.57,0:22:30.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And Tomoe...!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.53,0:22:36.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmph. Looks like all the poison hasn't been extracted yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.23,0:22:38.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}O-Oh no!! He'll become my familiar!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.69,0:22:39.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.19,0:22:42.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is Tomoe here?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.88,0:22:45.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard that Akura-ou is coming for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.77,0:22:52.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh yes... I must not get involved with Tomoe here.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.62,0:22:55.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If I had not become Yukiji-san's double,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.60,0:22:58.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}then it would have been Yukiji-san who met Tomoe here.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.04,0:23:02.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Could I have... perhaps... Yukiji-san and Tomoe's fate...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.13,0:23:08.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't give you to Akura-ou.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.50,0:23:10.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I will keep you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.60,0:23:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Do your best not to displease me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.85,0:23:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is the wicked Tomoe... of 500 years ago!!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.84,0:23:18.76,overlap dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait! Where are you taking me!?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.76,0:23:21.07,Default,,0,0,0,,The rain has stopped. We're going to my lair.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.22,0:23:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't your home!?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.43,0:23:24.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.89,0:23:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Just wait a moment! I mustn't go with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.56,0:23:33.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm really happy to have met you Tomoe,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.24,0:23:36.98,Default,,0,0,0,,but... I must return home.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.66,0:23:40.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}For the sake of meeting the Tomoe 500 years from now.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.32,0:23:44.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}In order to meet the you who calls me Nanami.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.78,0:23:46.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Your will has no meaning.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.45,0:23:51.43,Default,,0,0,0,,If I feel like it, I can turn you into ashes instantly.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.84,0:23:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You're just a toy that I shall treat as I please.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.42,0:23:58.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Be grateful that you are still alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.33,0:24:01.98,Default,,0,0,0,,STUPID FOOOX!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.08,0:24:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,When I say I'll return home, I {\i1}shall{\i0} do so!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.58,0:24:10.87,Default,,0,0,0,,And also, I hate the Tomoe who talks like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.48,0:24:14.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You hate me!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.12,0:24:17.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though you would have been killed by now if I wasn't here.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.28,0:24:20.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going back home because you hate me, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.19,0:24:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.92,0:24:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,That's amusing! Being unable to even stand due to the poison, how exactly are you planning to go home?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.35,0:24:27.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll manage somehow!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.05,0:24:31.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This woman...! This woman...! Shall I...!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.50,0:24:45.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, go ahead and try.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.84,0:24:53.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You should just die in this hovel alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.51,0:24:58.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Such a weak woman, alone in the depths of the mountains.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.44,0:25:01.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Just what exactly can she do when she can hardly walk?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.58,0:25:04.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She'll just give up overnight anyway.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.47,0:25:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}When that happens, she'll be more obedient.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.91,0:25:22.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And when she sees me, there's no doubt she'll come crying, "Tomoe-sama, please save me!"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.54,0:25:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She should know her place as an inconsequential being who must obey me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.62,0:25:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I hate the Tomoe who talks like that!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.86,0:25:35.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}For those words to pierce me this deeply...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.97,0:25:37.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Just who {\i0}is{\i1} that woman!?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.44,0:25:42.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Humans in the midst of such mountains?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.83,0:25:44.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Bandits, eh?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.99,0:25:46.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.34,0:25:50.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought that the house was in a strange location. So it's a thieves' den...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.36,0:25:52.66,Default,,0,0,0,,So cold...!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.77,0:25:57.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That Tomoe is no different from Akura-ou.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.88,0:26:01.54,Default,,0,0,0,,No, Tomoe is different!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.20,0:26:05.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually he's... always been more gentler.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.81,0:26:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! What's this!? A woman's sleepin' here.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.43,0:26:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}T-Those are some dangerous looking guys.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.52,0:26:15.28,Default,,0,0,0,,P-Pardon the intrusion!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.72,0:26:20.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, I was poisoned a bit and so am unable to move my body...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.46,0:26:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,This one's good...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.17,0:26:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,She's a reward from heavens for our hard work.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.92,0:26:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No...! Tomoe!!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.13,0:26:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,See? You can't do anything on your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.00,0:26:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you so before.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.46,0:26:37.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Fox fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.51,0:26:39.51,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a youkai! Run!!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.08,0:26:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tomoe!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.44,0:26:48.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.11,0:26:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't kill him!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.45,0:26:51.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.03,0:26:55.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomoe is... different from Akura-ou!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.79,0:26:59.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Your a fox that understands people's pain, right!?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.61,0:27:11.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.88,0:27:14.95,Default,,0,0,0,,...say that you don't hate me.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.32,0:27:18.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Just what am I saying!?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.74,0:27:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't... hate you.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.35,0:27:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This feeling... what is it...?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.97,0:27:42.58,Romanji ED,,0,0,0,,Hakanaki yume ga sameyaranu mama
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.97,0:27:42.58,English ED,,0,0,0,,In a lingering, fleeting dream,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.06,0:27:48.60,Romanji ED,,0,0,0,,Hanabirao hitotsu yakusoku ni shita
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.06,0:27:48.60,English ED,,0,0,0,,we made a promise on the petal.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.05,0:27:54.66,Romanji ED,,0,0,0,,Namao wo younde sugao ni furete
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.05,0:27:54.66,English ED,,0,0,0,,Calling my name, touching me earnestly,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.11,0:28:00.67,Romanji ED,,0,0,0,,Shiranai toshitsuki umeru te no hira
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.11,0:28:00.67,English ED,,0,0,0,,for many years, your hands held mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.16,0:28:11.30,Romanji ED,,0,0,0,,Midareta kami wo nanimo iwazuni naoshite kureta
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.16,0:28:11.30,English ED,,0,0,0,,Without saying a word you fixed my disheveled hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.46,0:28:15.82,Romanji ED,,0,0,0,,Ne
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.46,0:28:15.82,English ED,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.42,0:28:22.63,Romanji ED,,0,0,0,,Sakurani kotoba toki no wakuraba
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.42,0:28:22.63,English ED,,0,0,0,,By the cherry blossoms' sacred words,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.63,0:28:28.40,Romanji ED,,0,0,0,,Oikaketeita anatano senaka
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.63,0:28:28.40,English ED,,0,0,0,,I'd been chasing your back.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.40,0:28:33.95,Romanji ED,,0,0,0,,Furimuita hitomi wa kagayasashikute
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.40,0:28:33.95,English ED,,0,0,0,,You turned around with gentle eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.70,0:28:40.46,Romanji ED,,0,0,0,,Senobi wo shitara todoku kigashita
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.70,0:28:40.46,English ED,,0,0,0,,If I tiptoed, I might reach you,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.72,0:28:46.60,Romanji ED,,0,0,0,,Sono kyori sae mo tada suki datta
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.72,0:28:46.60,English ED,,0,0,0,,Even from afar, my love in unwavering
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.60,0:28:52.12,Romanji ED,,0,0,0,,Hitogo tsunoru omoi, dakishimeta mama
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.60,0:28:52.12,English ED,,0,0,0,,My feelings get stronger, every time you hug me close.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.86,0:29:00.97,Romanji ED,,0,0,0,,Ikutsumono haru wo someteku
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.86,0:29:00.97,English ED,,0,0,0,,You brought color to many springtimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.72,0:29:10.28,Romanji ED,,0,0,0,,Binetsu no hibi gaa susaburu kaze ga
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.72,0:29:10.28,English ED,,0,0,0,,The mildly feverish days, the rough winds,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.80,0:29:16.34,Romanji ED,,0,0,0,,Hanabira wo tsuyoku irozukete ita
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.80,0:29:16.34,English ED,,0,0,0,,were strongly coloring the petals.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.84,0:29:22.40,Romanji ED,,0,0,0,,Isakai wo shite mata yorisotte
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.84,0:29:22.40,English ED,,0,0,0,,We fought then cuddled close to each other,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.87,0:29:28.46,Romanji ED,,0,0,0,,Dochiraga tomonaku tsunagu te no hida
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.87,0:29:28.46,English ED,,0,0,0,,Somewhere along the line our hands got linked together.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.75,0:29:41.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(685,120)}Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.04,0:29:33.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomoe's special feelings for Nanami grew.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.15,0:29:36.71,Default,,0,0,0,,But Nanami's existence is something that shouldn't be in this era.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.98,0:29:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time, The God Goes to Meet.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.04,0:29:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,The Past Arc finale shall set your hearts racing until the end!
